thought of courage

1166
01:18:28,324 --> 01:18:32,827
as charging enemy bunkers
or standing up under fire.

1167
01:18:32,927 --> 01:18:38,862
But just to walk, day after day
from village to village

1168
01:18:38,962 --> 01:18:43,496
and through the paddies
and up into the mountains,

1169
01:18:43,596 --> 01:18:47,765
just to get up in the morning
and look out at the land

1170
01:18:47,865 --> 01:18:51,467
and think, "In a few minutes
I'll be walking out there

1171
01:18:51,567 --> 01:18:54,701
"and will my corpse be there,
over there?

1172
01:18:54,801 --> 01:18:56,235
Will I lose a leg out there?"

1173
01:18:58,036 --> 01:19:01,804
Just to walk felt
incredibly brave.

1174
